(\mathkw{push}\xi)[v/x] & otherwise
\end{cases}
~

~ MathPre
\mathkw{copyout} \xi (x:t,d) e = \begin{cases} \mathkw{pop} \xi & d = @in
\mathkw{pop} \xi & d = @none \land \xi(X) \neq @extern X \dots
\mathkw{pop} \xi & d = @none \land \xi(.X) \neq @extern X \dots
